1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 7=

4
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:19,440
Master, what level are you at now?

5
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,199
Ninth level?

6
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,079
But before I came down the mountain,

7
00:00:28,079 --> 00:00:29,079
my master warned me

8
00:00:29,079 --> 00:00:30,199
not to abuse my skills

9
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:31,480
or invite trouble.

10
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:33,799
Lin actually thought

11
00:00:33,799 --> 00:00:35,600
I had no inner force

12
00:00:35,679 --> 00:00:36,880
and still picked a fight with me.

13
00:00:37,679 --> 00:00:38,359
What a joke.

14
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:40,399
Ninth level?

15
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,719
Greetings,

16
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:50,759
(Sang Wuqi, Jiuyou Judge of Demon Sect)
Mr. Sang.

17
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:53,640
(Sang Wuqi, Jiuyou Judge of Demon Sect)
Where are Sang Yan and Sang Yu?

18
00:00:53,759 --> 00:00:56,000
Those precious disciples of yours

19
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:59,560
are probably fertilizer by now.

20
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:01,439
Who did it?

21
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,159
We only know his name is Peng Dasheng.

22
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,159
We know nothing about his background.

23
00:01:06,799 --> 00:01:08,359
Peng Dasheng.

24
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,959
Find him immediately.

25
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:13,640
I'll sacrifice him
in memory of my disciples.

26
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,280
You scheming old woman.

27
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,159
You knew they were dead all along.

28
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:20,159
What are you up to?

29
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:23,879
Master ordered us to lie low

30
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:27,680
until the Murong family's
martial tournament.

31
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:30,519
But he never said

32
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:33,599
we couldn't take lives.

33
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,239
What do you mean?

34
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,400
What do I mean?

35
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:43,280
(Nether Marionette, Demon Sect)
If we wipe out every young talent here

36
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:45,879
and strike fear into
the entire martial world,

37
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:50,000
wouldn't that earn us
great favor with our master?

38
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:53,680
You want me to do your killing for you.

39
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:57,120
What does that have
to do with my disciples?

40
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:59,519
What if I told you

41
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:03,200
the man who killed your disciples

42
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:08,599
will also be entering
the martial tournament at Murong Manor?

43
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:11,520
Murong Manor is full of top fighters.

44
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:14,400
How sure are you?

45
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:19,599
I can lure the guards away.

46
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:28,599
Xiao Ziting pays his respects
to you both.

47
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,400
Here.

48
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:34,800
Let's go.

49
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,199
Stop.

50
00:02:36,879 --> 00:02:38,199
Servants and deliveries
use the back gate.

51
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:39,599
Don't you know the rules?

52
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,919
I'm here for the martial tournament.

53
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,080
Where's your entry letter?

54
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,400
What entry letter?

55
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:48,000
Anyone entering the martial tournament

56
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,479
must present a letter

57
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:51,719
sealed by the head of their sect.

58
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,199
Don't tell me you didn't know that.

59
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,280
Move along.

60
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,159
Stop blocking the gate.

61
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,319
You could've stayed away,

62
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,800
but you came looking for trouble.

63
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:06,400
Peng Dasheng,
you really have a death wish, don't you?

64
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:09,879
Looks like wiping out the Sihai Gang

65
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,800
wasn't enough of a lesson.

66
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,159
Sihai Gang?

67
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,319
It was nothing but a lapdog

68
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:17,319
begging at my feet.

69
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,479
If one dies, I'll replace it.

70
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,719
You think I cared?

71
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,400
Then whose lapdog are you?

72
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:29,000
Peng Dasheng!

73
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,960
You think I won't end you right here?

74
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:35,319
Go ahead and try.

75
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:35,960
You!

76
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:38,080
You're such a pain!

77
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,000
If Mr. Murong finds out

78
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,800
you drew your blade outside his manor

79
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,039
and broke martial rules,

80
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:45,159
you won't even get into

81
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,879
today's tournament.

82
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,840
Letting you die today

83
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,639
would be too easy on you.

84
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:58,240
I'll win this martial tournament

85
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:00,639
and proudly take Murong Bingqing
as my bride.

86
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:04,199
Let's not talk about
who lives or dies just yet.

87
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,039
What makes you so sure

88
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:08,240
you'll win the tournament?

89
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,439
What a joke.

90
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,639
You can't even get through

91
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,479
the Murong family's gate,

92
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:14,199
and you're talking about winning?

93
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,079
Who says he can't get in?

94
00:04:26,639 --> 00:04:28,600
(Primordial Token)
Nongxiao Pavilion's Primordial Tokens.

95
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,160
(Primordial Token)
Dasheng and I each have one.

96
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,839
Will that do?

97
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:40,040
The famed Nongxiao Pavilion of Jiangbei?

98
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:41,680
And you are?

99
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:44,160
I'm Xiao Ziting,
the heir of Nongxiao Pavilion.

100
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:46,680
Take a good look.

101
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,079
These Primordial Tokens

102
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:50,000
were carved from ancient mystic jade

103
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,959
found atop Kunlun.

104
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,279
Only two exist in the world.

105
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,000
Since he's your friend,

106
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,199
there's no problem.

107
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,759
You may both enter.

108
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,839
Mr. Xiao, please wait.

109
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,399
I've long admired
your father's reputation.

110
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,040
I'm...

111
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,839
I know who you are.

112
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,480
Lin Dun of Huxiao Manor,

113
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,120
the notorious spoiled heir.

114
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:14,040
Everyone's heard of you.

115
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:17,480
Let's go.

116
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,079
You three, stop right there!

117
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:21,959
Peng Dasheng,

118
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:25,240
don't think Nongxiao Pavilion's backing

119
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,839
makes you untouchable.

120
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,839
Let me tell you something.

121
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:29,759
Here in Gusu,

122
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,240
Huxiao Manor

123
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,839
answers to no one.

124
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,800
(Peng Dasheng...)

125
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:42,040
(I swear I'll tear you limb from limb.)

126
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,279
I'll win in the end.

127
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:56,860
(Martial Tournament)

128
00:05:56,860 --> 00:05:58,140
(Champion)

129
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,800
It's the Murong family's

130
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,360
big martial tournament today.

131
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,800
Why isn't Mr. Murong here?

132
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:13,360
I heard there was trouble
at Chenghuang Temple outside the city.

133
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,920
He took some men to investigate.

134
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,439
What's he doing here?

135
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,920
Young men and fellow martial artists,

136
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:34,199
(Han Qiaosheng, All-Knowing Scholar)
I'm Han Qiaosheng, All-Knowing Scholar.

137
00:06:34,439 --> 00:06:35,399
Next...

138
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:39,399
Hey, I almost
forgot to introduce myself.

139
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:45,040
(Bai Yiwei, Wudang Sect's Daoist)
I'm Bai Yiwei, Wudang's One-Brow Daoist.

140
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:49,279
Who hasn't heard
of the famous One-Brow Daoist?

141
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,279
Last year,

142
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,079
Ms. Kongji of Emei Sect

143
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:54,959
heard your dual-cultivation method
was remarkable.

144
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,879
She secretly met you in your quarters
at midnight to compare techniques,

145
00:06:57,879 --> 00:06:59,839
only to be caught by a young Daoist.

146
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:02,199
Humiliated,
Ms. Kongji left the order for good.

147
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,399
To this day,

148
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:07,480
it's still one of the martial world's
favorite scandals.

149
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,879
You... You...

150
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,360
Dasheng,

151
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,839
the One-Brow Daoist looks nearly fifty.

152
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,600
Who knew he still had
that much fire in him?

153
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:23,439
What's so surprising?

154
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:26,279
My master's in his forties,

155
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,959
and he wakes up raring to go
every single day.

156
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,800
Now that's vigor.

157
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,319
Raring to do what?

158
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,079
Qiaosheng!

159
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,439
You lost at cards last night.

160
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,199
Are you still going on about it?

161
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:50,600
You old Daoist.

162
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:52,759
I haven't even aired
your dirtiest secrets.

163
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:54,879
That's me showing mercy.

164
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:02,199
Everyone, we were only joking.

165
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:04,600
We were invited here today

166
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:07,040
to serve as commentators
for this martial tournament.

167
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,600
We're deeply honored.

168
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,079
We've also invited

169
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:12,079
eight veteran martial masters

170
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:13,279
to serve as judges

171
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:15,240
and ensure fairness.

172
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:17,040
I now declare

173
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:19,480
the martial tournament
is officially open.

174
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,600
Begin!

175
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,560
Wait.

176
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:40,600
I'm Lin Dun, the heir of Huxiao Manor.

177
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,759
May I ask the elders

178
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,799
whether there are any requirements

179
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:46,840
for today's contestants?

180
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:48,879
None.

181
00:08:49,039 --> 00:08:50,440
By martial tradition,

182
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,879
any sect listed

183
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:55,000
in the martial registry

184
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,440
may send disciples to compete.

185
00:08:58,759 --> 00:09:02,039
What if someone uses another sect's name

186
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:03,960
to sneak into the tournament?

187
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,039
What then?

188
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,399
By martial tradition,

189
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,759
his meridians must be severed,

190
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,960
his cultivation stripped,

191
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:12,480
and he must be barred
from the martial world for life.

192
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:15,679
Then I ask the elders to bear witness.

193
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:18,879
The impostor I mentioned

194
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,480
is this man right here.

195
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,039
Young man.

196
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:42,440
Is everything Mr. Lin said true?

197
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,360
Every word is true.

198
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,879
(What is Peng Dasheng trying to do?)

199
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,840
You all heard him.

200
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,639
What are you waiting for?

201
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:03,440
Hold it.

202
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,559
She must be

203
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:14,600
Miss Murong Bingqing.

204
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:27,279
This man has ties to my family.

205
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:30,559
He may have entered
under false pretenses,

206
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,399
but that hardly warrants
such punishment.

207
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,879
I ask the elders to show mercy

208
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,600
and spare him.

209
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:42,480
Wouldn't that violate martial rules?

210
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:46,480
Since today's tournament
is being held for the Murong family,

211
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:48,639
we should follow the host's wishes.

212
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,039
We'll leave his fate

213
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,679
to you, Miss Murong.

214
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,000
Agreed.

215
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:57,679
Peng Dasheng,

216
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,279
please leave.

217
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:03,440
Never set foot in Gusu again.

218
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:07,759
You hear that?

219
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:10,120
If Miss Murong hadn't

220
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,000
pleaded for you,

221
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,480
you'd have lost
all your cultivation by now.

222
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,639
Now get out.

223
00:11:20,039 --> 00:11:21,879
Let me make one thing clear.

224
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:24,399
No matter who tries to stop me today

225
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:27,480
or how they try to keep me
out of this martial tournament,

226
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:30,080
I will not back down.

227
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,159
Big talk.

228
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,480
Are you Peng Dasheng?

229
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,960
That's right.

230
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,600
Mr. Murong,

231
00:12:17,679 --> 00:12:18,879
this man is arrogant and reckless.

232
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:19,799
He has no respect for anyone.

233
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,080
You can't let him off lightly.

234
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:23,679
You have some nerve!

235
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,440
You hear that?

236
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,639
You've got some nerve!

237
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,080
Kneel and apologize!

238
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,879
Mr. Murong, you hit the wrong man.

239
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:34,600
He's Peng Dasheng.

240
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:36,159
I meant to hit you.

241
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,639
At Chenghuang Temple,

242
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,960
Peng Dasheng single-handedly defeated

243
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,639
the Northern Evil Duo of the Demon Sect.

244
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:45,080
He did the martial world
a great service.

245
00:12:46,679 --> 00:12:48,240
He's a true young hero.

246
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:49,960
You disrespected him,

247
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:51,399
so you deserved that slap.

248
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,440
That...

249
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,159
That's impossible.

250
00:12:54,159 --> 00:12:54,440
He...

251
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:57,799
He's just a poor nobody
from some tiny sect.

252
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:59,879
How could he defeat
the Northern Evil Duo?

253
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:04,240
Mr. Peng,

254
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:07,799
you claim you defeated
the Northern Evil Duo,

255
00:13:08,279 --> 00:13:11,200
but many here have their doubts.

256
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,639
Since today is my daughter's
martial tournament,

257
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,879
would you care to prove yourself
in the ring?

258
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:17,879
I didn't come here today

259
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:19,440
just for the martial tournament.

260
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:21,639
I came to show everyone
what I'm made of.

261
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:23,279
Even if no one doubted me,

262
00:13:23,679 --> 00:13:26,080
I'd still take the title today.

263
00:13:27,799 --> 00:13:29,559
I admire your spirit.

264
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,000
If you truly win today,

265
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:36,240
I won't care about your background.

266
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,679
I'll announce it
to the entire martial world.

267
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,399
But if you lose...

268
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,159
If I lose,

269
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,440
I'll sever my own meridians,

270
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,639
give up my cultivation,

271
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,879
and leave the martial world forever.

272
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,879
Then let's see what you've got.

273
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:58,000
Please begin the tournament at once.

274
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:01,780
(Martial Tournament)

275
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:11,159
Everyone, listen closely.

276
00:14:11,159 --> 00:14:13,679
This martial tournament
has three rounds.

277
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:16,080
The first round is unarmed combat.

278
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,360
It ends when the incense is out.

279
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,879
Choose your own opponents.

280
00:14:19,879 --> 00:14:21,240
The losers leave the arena.

281
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:24,399
The round ends
when only six fighters remain.

282
00:14:24,399 --> 00:14:26,440
(Martial Tournament)
Guys, begin!

283
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,480
Every fighter is showing off
his best moves.

284
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:55,240
What a gathering of talent.

285
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,360
It's been years

286
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:58,159
since I've seen a crowd this lively.

287
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,559
He truly deserves the name
Flying Dragon Swordsman.

288
00:15:01,559 --> 00:15:03,320
That footwork is...

289
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:04,679
Wait.

290
00:15:04,679 --> 00:15:06,480
Is... is he biting him?

291
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,279
What a shame.

292
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,840
Kunlun's top disciple

293
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:21,480
(Out)
is out in the very first round.

294
00:15:22,279 --> 00:15:23,600
Flying Dog...

295
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,240
Oh, I mean...

296
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:26,679
He may have to give up
the title of Flying Dragon.

297
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,559
What is Peng Dasheng doing?

298
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,480
He hasn't moved

299
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:42,559
since the match began.

300
00:15:42,799 --> 00:15:44,279
Did he have a stroke?

301
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:45,600
In my opinion,

302
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,960
he's conserving his strength.

303
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,080
But the round's almost over.

304
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:52,080
He's running out of time.

305
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,440
Dasheng, watch out!

306
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:22,500
♪Come on♪

307
00:16:24,879 --> 00:16:26,679
It... it's over already?

308
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,159
With barely any time left,

309
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:29,720
he still turned it around
without breaking a sweat.

310
00:16:29,919 --> 00:16:33,879
Peng Dasheng is the real deal.

311
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:38,740
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

312
00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:41,660
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

313
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:47,700
♪Come on♪

314
00:16:51,220 --> 00:16:52,900
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

315
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:57,820
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

316
00:16:58,100 --> 00:17:01,020
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

317
00:17:01,260 --> 00:17:04,100
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

318
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:07,100
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

319
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:10,580
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

320
00:17:10,820 --> 00:17:13,820
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

321
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:16,900
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

322
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:19,820
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

323
00:17:20,380 --> 00:17:23,700
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

324
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:26,740
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

325
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:32,420
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

326
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,860
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

327
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:37,940
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

328
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:41,060
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

329
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:44,860
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

330
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:47,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

331
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:50,620
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

332
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:54,060
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

333
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:58,380
♪I am my own king♪

334
00:18:11,460 --> 00:18:13,020
♪I emerge into the world♪

335
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:14,780
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

336
00:18:14,780 --> 00:18:16,140
♪My pride is my trump card♪

337
00:18:16,140 --> 00:18:17,940
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

338
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:19,340
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

339
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:21,100
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

340
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,620
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

341
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,340
♪I dare to break every rule♪

342
00:18:24,340 --> 00:18:25,660
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

343
00:18:25,660 --> 00:18:27,500
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

344
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:28,740
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

345
00:18:28,740 --> 00:18:30,980
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

346
00:18:30,980 --> 00:18:32,500
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

347
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:34,100
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

348
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:35,700
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

349
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:37,420
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

350
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:39,140
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

351
00:18:39,140 --> 00:18:40,500
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

352
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:42,140
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

353
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:43,620
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

354
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:45,340
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

355
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,940
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

356
00:18:46,940 --> 00:18:48,500
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

357
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:52,820
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

358
00:18:52,820 --> 00:18:54,980
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

359
00:18:54,980 --> 00:18:57,580
♪Let me write the legend♪

360
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:05,020
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

361
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:08,340
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

362
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:10,820
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

363
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:14,900
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

364
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:17,860
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

365
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:20,340
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

366
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:23,380
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

367
00:19:23,380 --> 00:19:28,420
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
